## 🔥 Dynamic Waste Heatmaps
Heatmaps update based on:
- Time of day
- Weekday / Weekend / Holiday
- Public events and festivals

### Color Indicators
- 🟢 Green → Low waste density
- 🟠 Orange → Moderate waste density
- 🔴 Red → High waste density

---

## 🧠 Smart Bin Monitoring
Clicking any bin or area displays:
- Area name
- Place name
- Bin capacity
- Bin fill percentage
- Fill status:
  - Light Fill
  - Moderate Fill
  - Heavy Fill

